Je suis Alpha Favorise, artiste engagé,:
I am Alpha Favorise, a committed artist, passionate about the arts of speech and the transmission of stories. Driven by poetry, slam and storytelling, I am a multidisciplinary artist operating in the cultural field, capable of navigating between different forms of expression to touch and inspire the public.

 I founded the Collectif des artistes du Haut-Katanga, an initiative which aims to bring together, promote and promote local talents, defend their rights and provide a common platform for artistic expression and creativity.

 ✨ My vision is to make art a tool for social transformation, education and cultural influence, so that the creativity of Haut-Katanga inspires well beyond our borders.

 🎯 My goals are to:

 Give a strong and credible voice to the artists of our province;

 Create innovative and inclusive cultural projects;

 Promote exchanges between generations and artistic disciplines;

 Raise public awareness of the importance of culture as living heritage;

 Contribute to the emergence of a strong and recognized cultural identity.

 Through my projects, I seek to inspire, raise awareness and celebrate the cultural richness of our territory, by making art a driver of unity, pride and hope.
